{"tid":1489034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8.24 入觀塘的「Dress Code」","createTime":"2019-08-19T18:43:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T20:04:51.000Z","uid":278506,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"72f65ac7b1faf434711e0e87a136a6c90c5828b5","tid":1489034,"uid":278506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:43:57.000Z","msg":"警告!警告! 除了五大訴求缺一不可!<br />\n8.24 入觀塘活動更有地區性議題「監控燈柱」!!! <br />\n<br />\n你以為「監控燈柱」只實裝了在<em>啟德、九龍灣</em>MegaBox附近和<em>觀塘</em>? 咁就錯Q晒啦~ 在過去幾星期各個MTR, 和遊行路線都緊急加工裝了好多波波Cam，唔理襯唔襯核撚凸凸都照裝!!!!<br />\n唔信行街時留意下，試下<ins>影低post圖推post</ins>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zeXgGNM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzeXgGNM.jpg&h=e50c0872&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「監控燈柱」和邪惡Cam能高清拍攝，輔以人面識別技術準確由「面相」、「耳廓」和「步姿」準確認到你；<br />\n臨落車先上口罩? sorry你上車前已影到你~<br />\n一出門口就戴咗口罩? sorry 你無遮到耳仔都認到你~</span><br />\n<br />\n所以!!! <br />\n8.24 觀塘活動, 無論你<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和理非</span>定<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">勇武</span>, 請black bloc之餘<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「包埋你個頭」</span>, <br />\nor 放下長髮,<br />\nor戴大大個headphone~ <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「總之不露臉不露耳」, 表示對自身私隱行踪嘅關注, 和突顯監控Cam的荒謬！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VAaxZBb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVAaxZBb.jpg&h=d1e675ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nKnow more:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AntiCCTV/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FAntiCCTV%2F&d=OqNKNX3jJWm7Bj